strings: That meddlesome old hag! Trying to cheat me of my destiny!? Argh, my eyes, my eyes...!

But now only one seal remains. Just one more... When the last sage's heir is buried,
it will all be over!

<se_high>Jessica: Stop where you are!
You aren't getting away this time!
<se_low>Yangus: Oi! You ain't gettin' off the 'ook that easy!
<se_def>Angelo: Stop! We'll put an end to this here and now!
